Method 1
lex pgm.l>pgm.c
gcc pgm.c -o outputfilename
./outputfilename [command line args] 		//[] indicates optional

Method 2:

lex pgm.l
gcc lex.yy.c -o outputfilename
./outputfilename [command line args]            //[] indicates optional

If output file name is not provided, the default output file is named a.out
